an><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"%d %d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>m<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">scanf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"%1d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">getResult</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"%d \\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">refillArr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> n <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> m <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  n<span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  m<span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">isEmpty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">getResult</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token function\">isEmpty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> n <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> m <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">refillArr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">getResult</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>해결 방법</h3>\n<p>첫 풀이 방법은 다이나믹 프로그래밍 기법을 사용한 것이라고는 볼 수 없는 코드이다.</p>\n<p>오히려 단순 재귀 호출 풀이인데, 이 문제를 보고 처음으로 든 생각은 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>처음부터 끝까지 돌면서 자기 자신, 바로 우측 칸, 아래 칸, 우측 대각선 아래 칸이 모두 1일 경우, 해당 자리는 1로 채운다.</p>\n<p>1로 채운 후에는 맨 우측줄과 맨 아랫줄은 더 이상 사용하지 않으므로 가로, 세로 길이를 1씩 줄인다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>해당 범위 내의 숫자가 모두 0이거나, 가로 또는 세로 둘 중 하나의 길이가 0인 경우 재귀를 탈출한다.</p>\n<p>1이 남아있다는 말은 그 지점으로부터 길이가 2인 정사각형이 존재한다는 말이다.</p>\n<p>따라서 모두 0이 될 때 까지 반복한다면 그 반복 횟수로 정사각형의 최대 길이를 알 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>백준 예시로 과정을 그려보자면,</p>\n<br />\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 718px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/58568d1b475aaaf3a20fd7be83d227e5/ab030/problem-solving-review-1915-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.770833333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/58568d1b475aaaf3a20fd7be83d227e5/a59e9/problem-solving-review-1915-1.webp 192w,\n/static/58568d1b475aaaf3a20fd7be83d227e5/0ca9f/problem-solving-review-1915-1.webp 384w,\n/static/58568d1b475aaaf3a20fd7be83d227e5/3b4cc/problem-solving-review-1915-1.webp 718w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 718px) 100vw, 718px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/58568d1b475aaaf3a20fd7be83d227e5/3b721/problem-solving-review-1915-1.png 192w,\n/static/58568d1b475aaaf3a20fd7be83d227e5/66595/problem-solving-review-1915-1.png 384w,\n/static/58568d1b475aaaf3a20fd7be83d227e5/ab030/problem-solving-review-1915-1.png 718w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 718px) 100vw, 718px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/58568d1b475aaaf3a20fd7be83d227e5/ab030/problem-solving-review-1915-1.png\"\n            alt=\"Attached Photo 1\"\n            title=\"Attached Photo 1\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br />\n<p>다음과 같이 0이 될 때까지 반복하면 한 변의 최대 길이는 2라는 것을 알 수 있다.</p>\n<p>하지만, 이 풀이 방법은 다이나믹 프로그래밍 기법을 사용하지도 않을 뿐더러, 매번 처음부터 끝까지 순회해야 한다는 점에서 시간적으로 매우 비효율적인 방법이다.</p>\n<p>만약 사이즈가 더 크거나, 제한 시간이 더 짧았더라면 시간 초과가 발생했을 풀이 방법이다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>추가 풀이</h2>\n<h3>다이나믹 프로그래밍 풀이 방법</h3>\n<p>먼저 첫 번째 실마리는 정사각형의 내부는 모두 1로 채워져있다는 것이다.</p>\n<p>따라서 1행 1열부터 마지막행 마지막열까지 순회하면서 해당 위치로부터 왼쪽 1칸, 위쪽 1칸, 왼쪽 윗 방향 대각선 1칸으로부터 최대 정사각형의 길이를 구하여 해당 위치 값에 추가할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>그림으로 나타내면 다음과 같다.</p>\n<br />\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 691px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa38b27682c3b79cd5c90f9a5bdc3158/2928f/problem-solving-review-1915-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.8125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/aa38b27682c3b79cd5c90f9a5bdc3158/a59e9/problem-solving-review-1915-2.webp 192w,\n/static/aa38b27682c3b79cd5c90f9a5bdc3158/0ca9f/problem-solving-review-1915-2.webp 384w,\n/static/aa38b27682c3b79cd5c90f9a5bdc3158/366f1/problem-solving-review-1915-2.webp 691w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 691px) 100vw, 691px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/aa38b27682c3b79cd5c90f9a5bdc3158/3b721/problem-solving-review-1915-2.png 192w,\n/static/aa38b27682c3b79cd5c90f9a5bdc3158/66595/problem-solving-review-1915-2.png 384w,\n/static/aa38b27682c3b79cd5c90f9a5bdc3158/2928f/problem-solving-review-1915-2.png 691w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 691px) 100vw, 691px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/aa38b27682c3b79cd5c90f9a5bdc3158/2928f/problem-solving-review-1915-2.png\"\n            alt=\"Attached Photo 2\"\n            title=\"Attached Photo 2\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br />\n<p>계속 순회하면서 이 방법을 적용하면 다음과 같이 최대 정사각형의 길이를 도출할 수 있다.</p>\n<br />\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 685px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/52c821a8a391b15012d277e74dcff942/a31f0/problem-solving-review-1915-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.29166666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/52c821a8a391b15012d277e74dcff942/a59e9/problem-solving-review-1915-3.webp 192w,\n/static/52c821a8a391b15012d277e74dcff942/0ca9f/problem-solving-review-1915-3.webp 384w,\n/static/52c821a8a391b15012d277e74dcff942/ef8ff/problem-solving-review-1915-3.webp 685w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 685px) 100vw, 685px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/52c821a8a391b15012d277e74dcff942/3b721/problem-solving-review-1915-3.png 192w,\n/static/52c821a8a391b15012d277e74dcff942/66595/problem-solving-review-1915-3.png 384w,\n/static/52c821a8a391b15012d277e74dcff942/a31f0/problem-solving-review-1915-3.png 685w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 685px) 100vw, 685px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/52c821a8a391b15012d277e74dcff942/a31f0/problem-solving-review-1915-3.png\"\n            alt=\"Attached Photo 3\"\n            title=\"Attached Photo 3\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br />\n<p>이렇게 그림으로 볼 수 있듯이 해당 자리의 숫자는 그 자리로부터 왼쪽 방향과 윗쪽 방향으로 최대 해당 길이로 정사각형을 만들 수 있다는 뜻이기 때문에 세 자리의 최소값을 해당 자리에 더해주면 된다.</p>\n<p>만약 해당 자리가 0인 경우에는 어떠한 경우에도 정사각형이 생길 수 없기 때문에 넘어가주면 된다.</p>\n<p>따라서 다음과 같은 점화식을 세울 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">dp<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> dp<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">min</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dp<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> dp<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> dp<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> dp<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이 과정을 통해 변경한 배열에서 구한 최대값은 주어진 환경에서 만들 수 있는 최대 크기의 정사각형 길이를 뜻하므로 이를 제곱하여 출력하면 된다.</p>\n<p>아래는 다이나믹 프로그래밍 풀이 방법으로 바꾼 코드이다.</p>\n<h3>해당 방법으로 바꾼 소스 코드</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;iostream></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;cmath></span></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> std<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">threeMin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">calcMaxSize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">scanf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"%d %d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>m<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">scanf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"%1d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">calcMaxSize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> maxSize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      maxSize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>maxSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"%d \\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> maxSize <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> maxSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">threeMin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">min</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">min</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">calcMaxSize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token function\">threeMin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>풀이 결과</h3>\n<p>채점 결과, 다음과 같이 약 6배 정도의 시간 차이가 발생했다.</p>\n<p>위의 결과가 최초로 AC 받았을 때의 코드이고, 다음 코드는 다이나믹 프로그래밍 방법으로 개선한 코드이다.</p>\n<br />\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/e9d40/problem-solving-review-1915-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 3.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAIAAABR8BlyAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAPUlEQVQI1zXJMQ6AMAwDQP7/QHaGDBQSVJfKicUAC7feUnpy7ObbnTpHX5tZD0n1I+lHS6CkK4LAt5h0zBfE5zj7jB1eaQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/a59e9/problem-solving-review-1915-4.webp 192w,\n/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/0ca9f/problem-solving-review-1915-4.webp 384w,\n/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/dc9b9/problem-solving-review-1915-4.webp 768w,\n/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/be29d/problem-solving-review-1915-4.webp 1014w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/3b721/problem-solving-review-1915-4.png 192w,\n/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/66595/problem-solving-review-1915-4.png 384w,\n/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/fe486/problem-solving-review-1915-4.png 768w,\n/static/bc03ea2197954fddb3c6021cc8e0f43e/e9d40/problem-solving-review-1915-4.png 1014w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n        